### Register user

POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "something@email.com",
  "password": "verysecurepassword"
}


### Login user

POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "something@email.com",
  "password": "verysecurepassword"
}
